01/regulation/10">10</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-e6ea998609d50f91a456e0abe7e55019" marker="F149"><p>Reg. 11(2)(3) omitted (6.4.2012) by virtue of <ref eId="cwhox9193-00016" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2012/848">The Tax Credits (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2012 (S.I. 2012/848)</ref>, <ref eId="cwhox9193-00017" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2012/848/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="cwhox9193-00018" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2012/848/regulation/2/15/a">2(15)(a)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-baf0fc950ac0ff31acf159ffd96e06c6" marker="F150"><p>Reg. 11(4) substituted (6.4.2009) by <ref eId="cqdpmb4j3-00008" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2009/697">The Tax Credits (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2009 (S.I. 2009/697)</ref>, <ref eId="cqdpmb4j3-00009" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2009/697/regulation/1/c">regs. 1(c)</ref>, <ref eId="cqdpmb4j3-00010" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2009/697/regulation/4/1">4(1)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-6697cb7843c95740664fa015c4267b34" marker="F151"><p>Word in reg. 11(4) omitted (6.4.2012) by virtue of <ref eId="cwhox9193-00007" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2012/848">The Tax Credits (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2012 (S.I. 2012/848)</ref>, <ref eId="cwhox9193-00008" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2012/848/regulation/1/2">regs. 1(2)</ref>, <ref eId="cwhox9193-00009" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2012/848/regulation/2/15/b">2(15)(b)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-53468a1163a35f62041b452ccf3220cb" marker="F152"><p>Words in reg. 11(4) su