 F" eId="key-ae316482adb41f3314fb452e48c323cb" marker="F187"><p>Reg. 14(1A)(c) added (6.4.2006) by <ref eId="cq57rm833-00026" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2006/766">The Tax Credits (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2006 (S.I. 2006/766)</ref>, <ref eId="cq57rm833-00027" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2006/766/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="cq57rm833-00028" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2006/766/regulation/20/4">20(4)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-55e2b866b4e84e997e6604d71555c5e6" marker="F188"><p>Reg. 14(1A)(d) inserted (6.4.2007) by <ref eId="cq59749o3-00026" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2007/824">The Tax Credits (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2007 (S.I. 2007/824)</ref>, <ref eId="cq59749o3-00027" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2007/824/regulation/1">regs. 1</ref>, <ref eId="cq59749o3-00028" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2007/824/regulation/6/2">6(2)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-33f7f601c8413c09999c65eca9c053d5" marker="F189"><p>Words in reg. 14(1A)(d) substituted (21.11.2009) by <ref eId="cqm4wna23-00045" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2009/2887">The Tax Credits (Miscellaneous Amendments) (No. 2) Regulations 2009 (S.I. 2009/2887)</ref>, <ref eId="cqm4wna23-00046" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2009/2887/regulation/1/a">regs. 1(a)</ref>, <ref eId="cqm4wna23-00047" class="subref operative" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2009/2887/regulation/4/2/a">4(2)(a)</ref></p></note><note ukl:Name="Commentary" ukl:Type="F" class="commentary F" eId="key-9aeb9d90d66a9facdbc6c68eb9094f26" marker="F190"><p>Words in <ref eId="cr92vkz74-00006" class="subref" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2002/2005/regulation/14/1A/d">reg. 1